Great and handy for making any adjustments you need to do on any photos you 
take. Even if you don't know much about editing or photography apps. You 
can watch the demo clips that teach you quickly and easily. And if you want 
to use a feature that costs money, instead of buying it, you can watch a...Full ReviewGreat and handy for making any adjustments you need to do on any photos you 
take. Even if you don't know much about editing or photography apps. You 
can watch the demo clips that teach you quickly and easily. And if you want 
to use a feature that costs money, instead of buying it, you can watch an 
advertisement of 30 seconds and then get to use that particular feature for 
free up to 3 times.

I've had this app for over a year and it is absolutely amazing! One of the 
best pic editing apps I've used on a mobile phone. The only complaint I 
have and the reason I left one star off is because I noticed a glitch. Some 
of the features you have to either pay 99 cents or Share on your Facebook ...Full ReviewI've had this app for over a year and it is absolutely amazing! One of the 
best pic editing apps I've used on a mobile phone. The only complaint I 
have and the reason I left one star off is because I noticed a glitch. Some 
of the features you have to either pay 99 cents or Share on your Facebook 
to have complete access. I've noticed if I don't use the app for a couple 
of weeks, it resets and I have to Share it all over again. This didn't 
happen before the updates. It is inconvenient but the app is still great so 
it's worth it to keep. I won't pay for those features, however, because I'm 
afraid the app will reset and I'd have to keep paying for the same feature 
I already paid for. All in all, really awesome app. I would recommend it.
